Carnival Eats - Season 2, Episode 2




From Renaissance to Rio Grande

Young squire Noah Cappe tries his hand at making the King's Court Conch Fritters. Bidding adieu to his new friends, Noah heads west to Mercedes, Texas where the rough and ready cowboys and girls at the Livestock Show rustle up some western and Tex-Mex grub.




Original Air Date: 23-Jul-2015
